with you.

31
00:03:28,504 --> 00:03:30,699
At last we meet,
Professor Brainard.

32
00:03:30,773 --> 00:03:34,004
No, this is Professor Ashton.
He's Romance Languages.

33
00:03:34,077 --> 00:03:36,545
