I don't take sides.

41
00:03:58,401 --> 00:03:59,333
Betsy!

42
00:03:59,402 --> 00:04:01,802
Well, well,
here comes the bride.

43
00:04:01,871 --> 00:04:03,634
- Reverend.
- Good evening, sir.

44
00:04:03,706 --> 00:04:06,197
Professor Ashton
from Rutland University.

45
00:04:06,275 --> 00:04:08,243
